branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series AMD can separate and remove aerosol state oil mist in compressed air and remove carbon or dust of more than 0.01um. It should be used as prefilter for compressed air in precision instruments or for clean room requirements.
&lt;/p&gt;

